			<div><div class="">
    
<div class="rte">
<p>We have an <strong>EMERGENCY</strong> advice line which can be used out of office hours. This is for cases of harassment by a journalist or for pre-publication advice. It should not be used for general enquiries or to make a complaint. </p>
<p>24 Hour emergency advice line: 07799 903 929<br />(Please leave a message explaining the nature of your concern and you will be phoned back)</p>
<p>Media enquiries should be directed via email to <a href="mailto:john.davidson@ipso.co.uk">John Davidson</a>, Head of Communications.</p></div>
</div></div>
		</div>
	</div>



